OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,FA decade on from a damning report into
OL,7,Fmaternity services in Morecambe Bay
OL,8,Fits author says the "gross failure" of
OL,9,Fthe medical team that caused the death
OL,10,Fof a newborn baby girl is proof his
OL,11,Ffindings have been ignored.
OL,13,FDr Bill Kirkup was commissioned by the
OL,14,FGovernment to investigate a number of
OL,15,Fdeaths at the University Hospitals of
OL,16,FMorecambe Bay Trust's (UHMBT)
OL,17,Fmaternity wards between 2003 and 2013.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
