OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,FAfter a 19 day inquest, Lancashire's
OL,7,FSenior Coroner Dr James Adeley
OL,8,Fconcluded that her death was due to
OL,9,F"incompetence" from the midwifes and
OL,10,Fthose involved.
OL,12,FHe also indicated that failings
OL,13,Fidentified in the Kirkup report may
OL,14,F"not have been fully addressed".
OL,16,FSpeaking about the inquest, Dr Kirkup
OL,17,Fsaid: "Even in the same trust we're
OL,18,Fstill getting the same things wrong.
OL,19,FIt's unforgivable... but it's
OL,20,Funfortunately far too common.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
