OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1742667376
OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,F"But that doesn't excuse it or even
OL,7,Fexplain it. We do seem to struggle to
OL,8,Fget out of a mentality that says 'deny
OL,9,Feverything, it will make us look
OL,10,Fbetter.'
OL,12,F"But it never does. When the truth
OL,13,Femerges... You just look even worse."
OL,15,FIda's parents, Sarah Robinson and Ryan
OL,16,FLock, said they were made to feel like
OL,17,FIda's death was their fault by medical
OL,18,Fstaff, and questioned why the trust
OL,19,Fcould not have been more open.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
