OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,FIt echoed one of the key findings of
OL,7,FDr Kirkup's 2015 report, which said
OL,8,Fthere were "repeated failures to be
OL,9,Fhonest and open with patients,
OL,10,Frelatives, and others raising
OL,11,Fconcerns."
OL,13,FSpeaking after the inquest into Ida's
OL,14,Fdeath concluded, Dr Kirkup said:
OL,15,F"There should be early involvement
OL,16,Fwith the parents, they should get the
OL,17,Ffull information about what's gone
OL,18,Fwrong."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
