OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,FDr Kirkup argued not only was this
OL,7,Fimportant for the helping parents and
OL,8,Floved ones get closure, but will also
OL,9,Fhelp ensure mistakes are not repeated.
OL,11,FHe said: "There should be a proper
OL,12,Finvestigation so they know what
OL,13,Fhappened and so the clinical team can
OL,14,Fmake sure they don't keep doing the
OL,15,Fsame thing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
