OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1742667376
OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,F"You can design a system on a desktop
OL,7,Fthat appears to be okay, but if you
OL,8,Fput it in the real world... and then
OL,9,Fit fails, as it clearly has in this
OL,10,Fcase, then it clearly isn't fit for
OL,11,Fpurpose."
OL,13,FThe 2015 report found that work inside
OL,14,Fthe unit was found to be "seriously
OL,15,Fdysfunctional", with poor levels of
OL,16,Fclinical competence, extremely poor
OL,17,Fworking relationships, and a
OL,18,Fdetermination among midwives to pursue
OL,19,Fnormal childbirth "at any cost".
