OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,F"All of those things have failed in
OL,7,Fthis case, and this compounds the harm
OL,8,Fto Ida's family. It's bad enough
OL,9,Fwhat's happened to them."
OL,11,FDr Kirkup said the death of Ida Lock
OL,12,Fsuggests many of the recommendations
OL,13,Fhe made in 2015 have not been
OL,14,Fimplemented, and similar incidents are
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,17,FHe said: "What I can't say is if
OL,18,Fanything does go wrong I can guarantee
OL,19,Fthat people will get a full and honest
OL,20,Fexplanation and investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
