OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,FWhile Dr Kirkup described the UHMBT's
OL,7,Factions as "unforgivable", he believes
OL,8,Fthey are just part of a wider issue in
OL,9,Fhow all hospital's approach maternity
OL,10,Fcare.
OL,12,FHe said: "This is not restricted to
OL,13,FMorecambe Bay. This is a particularly
OL,14,Fhorrible example... but there are
OL,15,Fwidespread systemic failings in
OL,16,Fmaternity care. That much is obvious."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
