OL,3,CDeath of Baby Ida proof of 'systemic'
OL,4,Cfailings in maternity care
OL,6,FDr Adeley will send the report to the
OL,7,FSecretary of State for Health and the
OL,8,FChief Coroner, who will then decide
OL,9,Fwhether they would like to investigate
OL,10,Fthe issues raised.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Tabetha Darmon, Chief
OL,13,FNursing Officer of UHMBT, said:
OL,14,F"Losing a child is tragic and our
OL,15,Fheartfelt condolences go out to Ida's
OL,16,Fparents, family and loved ones. We are
OL,17,Ftruly sorry for the distress we have
OL,18,Fcaused.
